# FluxBill — backup guard so strategy/planning artifacts never enter the repo.
# The repo root is app/, so docs/, ACTION.md and the PDFs (one level up) are
# already outside it; this is belt-and-suspenders.

# Strategy / planning artifacts (must never be committed)
*.pdf
ACTION.md
/docs/
HACKATHON.md

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# Secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Node / build
node_modules/
dist/
